direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13

# --- Entry ---

entry: |md
  **/strat.refine**

  - Read `strat-tasks/`
  - YAML frontmatter
  - Business need (fixed)
| {style.fill: "#f5f5f5"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Check for prior reviews ---

check-reviews: |md
  **Check Reviews**

  - `strat-reviews/` exist?
  - Determines mode
| {style.fill: "#f5f5f5"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Architecture context (optional) ---

arch-context: |md
  **Architecture Context**

  - `.context/architecture-context/`
  - PLATFORM.md + components
  - Ground in real arch
| {style.fill: "#f5f5f5"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 1; style.stroke-dash: 3}

# --- Initial refinement ---

initial: |md
  **Initial Refinement**
  forked LLM agent

  - Technical approach
  - Affected components
  - Dependencies, NFRs
  - Effort estimate (S/M/L/XL)
  - Risks & open questions
| {style.fill: "#e8e8e8"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Revision mode ---

revision: |md
  **Revision Mode**
  forked LLM agent

  - Read review feedback
  - Address reviewer concerns
  - Preserve working parts
  - Flag disagreements
  - Document changes
| {style.fill: "#e8e8e8"; style.stroke: "#333333"; style.stroke-width: 2}

# --- Output ---

output: |md
  **Refined Strategy**

  - HOW complete
  - status → Refined
  - Ready for strat.review
| {style.fill: "#f5f5f5"; style.stroke: "#999999"; style.stroke-width: 1}

# --- Edges ---

entry -> check-reviews
check-reviews -> arch-context: "load context" {style.stroke-dash: 3}
arch-context -> initial: "no reviews" {style.stroke-dash: 3}
arch-context -> revision: "reviews exist" {style.stroke-dash: 3}
check-reviews -> initial: "no reviews"
check-reviews -> revision: "reviews exist"
initial -> output
revision -> output
